headline: 3 Consumer Stocks with Questionable Fundamentals
summary: Most consumer discretionary businesses succeed or fail based on the broader economy. Over the past six months, it seems like demand trends are working against their favor as the industry has tumbled by 5.8%. This drawdown was worse than the S&P 500’s 1% decline.
